# Web Development Guidelines

## Framework & Libraries

- **Next.js 15** with App Router
- **React 19** with modern hooks
- **Ant Design v5** for UI components
- **Tailwind CSS v4** for styling
- **SWR** for data fetching
- **TypeScript** with strict mode

## Project Structure

- **App Router**: `src/app/` - Next.js 15 app directory structure
- **Components**: `src/components/` - Reusable React components
- **API Layer**: `src/api/` - API client functions
- **Hooks**: `src/hooks/` - Custom React hooks
- **Utils**: `src/utils/` - Utility functions
- **Middleware**: [apps/web/src/middleware.ts](mdc:apps/web/src/middleware.ts) - Next.js middleware

## Component Guidelines

- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer TypeScript interfaces over types for props
- Use Ant Design components as base UI elements
- Customize Ant Design theme in [apps/web/src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/app/layout.tsx)
- Use [AntdNextRegistry](mdc:apps/web/src/components/systeam/AntdNextRegistry.tsx) for SSR compatibility

## Data Fetching

- Use SWR for client-side data fetching
- API functions in `src/api/` directory
- Request utility in [apps/web/src/utils/request.ts](mdc:apps/web/src/utils/request.ts)
- Automatic token handling and error management

## Styling

- Use Tailwind CSS for utility-first styling
- Custom CSS variables for theming in layout
- Ant Design components for complex UI elements
- Responsive design with Tailwind breakpoints

## Authentication

- JWT token stored in cookies
- Server-side token handling in [apps/web/src/utils/token.ts](mdc:apps/web/src/utils/token.ts)
- Protected routes using middleware
- Automatic redirect to login on token expiration

## Code Style

- Use TypeScript with strict mode
- Import shared types from `@repo/type`
- Use semicolons consistently
- Prefer named exports over default exports
- Use React 19 features (useMemo, useCallback when appropriate)
